[src:container-registry/spec-api-p02] This endpoint may also support RFC7233 compliant range requests.
[src:container-registry/spec-api-p02] Support can be detected by issuing a HEAD request.
[src:container-registry/spec-api-p02] If the header `Accept-Range: bytes` is returned, range requests can be used to fetch partial content.
[src:container-registry/spec-api-p02] The specified chunk of blob content will be present in the body of the request.
